To start using Bitnami Helm charts you need to accomplish the following prerequisites:

* You have a Kubernetes cluster running. Check out these [Get Started guides](/<%= platform_path %>) to setup a Kubernetes environment with ease.
* Your Kubernetes version is 1.12+.
* You have the [*kubectl command line (kubectl CLI)*](/<%= platform_path %>/faq/get-started/install-kubectl) installed.
* You have [Helm v3.x](/<%= platform_path %>/faq/get-started/install-configure-helm) installed.
